    "The similarity produced from this step is then used as an input for the matching and ranking step.",
    "Matching and rankingCVs for each job posting were ranked based on their cosine similarity scores obtained from the previous step.",
    "After the matching step, a CVs ranking is then held to produce a ranked list of CVs.",
    "The ranked list of CVs that gives the best matches of a job posting is the final output of the job matching module.",
    "Fast generic QAAccording to literature LSTM has proved to outperform other equivalent QA models [50]- [52]."
